 gender, age, tribe, ethnicity, disability or religion. \r\nThis organization is working under its constitution and is registered under the Societies Act with registration n° 551 October 2007, Law of Zanzibar n° 6/1995. \r\n\r\nThe objective of our Association is to help our poorest residents in developing the skills and resources they need through establishment and conduct of different activities related to social development and promotes the culture and heritage, in order to achieve a healthy lifestyle and sustainable livelihood of the people living in Zanzibar. This is because many people in Zanzibar are living on less than 1 $ per day, malnutrition is common, literacy levels are less than 60% in certain areas, and many residents lack access to basic health care, safe water and education.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for friends NGOs to work with in terms of getting Volunteers to volunteer in our Organization. We have different Programs and also we organize any activity for the interest of Volunteer for the Community Development.\r\n\r\nFor more information, please visit www.tziva.org, we are also want to replace a new website by anytime from now. Therefore, if found interesting please contact me with hmwinge@tziva.org or info@tziva.org.\r\n\r\nThank you\r\nRegards\r\n\r\nHussein A. Mwinge\r\nProgram and Project Coordinator\r\nTZIVA\r\nZanzibar, Tanzania\r\nP.O. Box 2249\r\nMalindi-Zanzibar\r\nTanzania\r\n','2013-03-02 01:14:41','2013-03-02 01:14:41'),(329,'Jaqueline Alejandra',' Cruz Barrios','jacb117@gmail.com','42128870','Necesito como me pueden ayudar mi primo de 18 años fue diagnosticado con Leucimia Linfocita aguda, y nosotros no contamos con muchos recursos, porfisss Dios se los pague ','2013-03-03 00:56:44','2013-03-03 00:56:44'),(330,'Mily','Chavarria','milychavarria@yahoo.es','','Buen dia, me gustaria integrarme a un voluntariado, ustedes manejan algun proceso en especial?\r\nSaludos','2013-03-04 14:52:51','2013-03-04 14:52:51'),(331,'Enma Gabriela ','Herrera 